DIRTY CUT 2025 - ISHAAN KHATTER 16/16

A standing ovation at Cannes for Homebound set the tone—Ishaan Khatter (@ishaankhatter) is playing for keeps. With The Perfect Couple and The Royals making him Gen Z’s favourite onscreen fixation, he’s choosing roles with range and keeping the charm turned all the way up. He might flirt with the chocolate boy image, but the filmography’s doing something smarter. For Dirty Cut 2025, the curls are still working—but so is the résumé.
